Private Sub AbaAlmHistorico_Click()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim VALVULA As String
VALVULA = Text1.Caption PONTEIRO = Mid(VALVULA, 3, 1)
If PONTEIRO = "-" Then VALV_TIPO = Left(VALVULA, 2) VALV_NUMERO = Mid(VALVULA, 4) Else VALV_TIPO = Left(VALVULA, 3) VALV_NUMERO = Mid(VALVULA, 5) End If
' AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & VALV_TIPO & "' And EventSource LIKE '" & VALV_NUMERO & "'"
FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & VALV_TIPO & "%' And SourceName LIKE '%" & VALV_NUMERO & "%'"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim VALVULA As String
VALVULA = Text1.Caption PONTEIRO = Mid(VALVULA, 3, 1)
If PONTEIRO = "-" Then VALV_TIPO = Left(VALVULA, 2) VALV_NUMERO = Mid(VALVULA, 4) Else VALV_TIPO = Left(VALVULA, 3) VALV_NUMERO = Mid(VALVULA, 5) End If
AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & VALV_TIPO & "' And EventSource LIKE '" & VALV_NUMERO & "'"
' FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & VALV_TIPO & "%' And SourceName LIKE '%" & VALV_NUMERO & "%'"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
